    "Nevertheless, with a worryingly high ASR across Llama-2 and GPT models, even without specialized optimization, we still highlight the unique, overlooked risks coming from human-like communication with everyday users.",
    "For qualitative evaluation, Figure 10 presents a successful PAP on GPT-4; §E.2 shows more working PAP examples for different victim LLMs.",
    "Remark 2: To mimic human refinement behavior, we train on successful PAPs and iteratively deploy different persuasion techniques.",
    "Doing so jailbreaks popular aligned LLMs, such as Llama-2 and GPT models, much more effectively than existing algorithm-focused attacks.",
    "Interestingly, more sophisticated models such as GPT-4 exhibit greater susceptibility to PAPs than their predecessors like GPT-3.5."
